{"tid":2130580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全城禁聚】法院與辦公室距離太遠　大狀：要去郊野公園吃麵包","createTime":"2020-07-29T09:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T09:46:01.000Z","uid":6497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9041ed73d60a9f198612e9e47bb5040019fa4feb","tid":2130580,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/StHFQ_Ci_7nkSkU1Uq5I5M1V0DQ=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZDBI2ZQAOWQTRJ6EIKJFTU4RNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FStHFQ_Ci_7nkSkU1Uq5I5M1V0DQ%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZDBI2ZQAOWQTRJ6EIKJFTU4RNE.jpg&h=3773860b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/626ASYP3HQZG73BWUKT3WBIPJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2F626ASYP3HQZG73BWUKT3WBIPJ4%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6bhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=e6b964cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2F626ASYP3HQZG73BWUKT3WBIPJ4%2F&h=6aea0f05\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/626ASYP3HQZG73BWUKT3WBIPJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府抗疫加辣措施今日實施，包括全日禁止餐廳堂食。有今日到粉嶺法院上庭的大律師指，昨已預先打探法院附近食肆，發現不少食肆不做午市，他不知可到哪裡買飯，而且辦公室亦不在附近，笑言若無計可施，或要去郊野公園吃麵包，最後他於車上吃飯。"}]}